      "content": "it's just... there's no point to anything. i go through the motions, i eat, i sleep, but there's no color in anything. it's like the version of me that actually lived died with him. what am i even doing here? just occupying space until i eventually disappear i guess. it feels so pointless to keep trying to build a life that isn't even mine anymore.",
